                          );
                        },
                        child: ClipRRect(
                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
                          child: Stack(
                            alignment: Alignment.bottomRight,
                            children: [
                              Image.file(_image!, fit: BoxFit.cover, width: double.infinity),
